  "detailed_description": "Welcome to the \"Rocky Ride\" solo developed arcade race!<br />\r\nYou’re about to see some cool maneuvers, unpredictable circuits, crazy speeds and dangerous rivals. A crazy race on a fast buggy car among steep rocks and dense forests.<br />\r\nYou need collect the items to win. Upgrade your buggy: make it faster and faster to go ahead! Pick any of the many different tracks, and go! To the prize points!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Various routes of the most fancy configurations<br />\r\n- Nice 3D graphics<br />\r\n- Realistic physics<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe game was made by one person, on enthusiasm. Programmed, drew models, etc.",
